data.text:
This list contains information on famous professional athletes with the most kids, loosely ranked by fame and popularity. Several famous football players, basketball stars, and boxers have four or more children. Some famous athletes have had all their kids with the same partner while other celebrity sports stars have had children with multiple partners. A few famous athletes have even adopted children.

Who will you find on this list of famous professional athletes with the most kids? Mike Tyson is near the top. The former heavy-weight champion has seven children with five different women. Tyson's kids include Mikey, Rayna, Amir, Miguel, Exodus, Milan, and Morocco. Fellow fighters Muhammad Ali and Evander Holyfield also have fathered several children.

NFL player Adrian Peterson has six children with multiple different women. Other famous athletes with lots of kids include Michael Jordan, Ray Lewis, and Dan Marino. Look to this list to also find out what type of athlete has the most kids!
